.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07094725/2022-sc-bronson-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07094725/2022-sc-bronson-800x601.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07094725/2022-sc-bronson-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07094725/2022-sc-bronson-768x577.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07094725/2022-sc-bronson-696x523.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07094725/2022-sc-bronson-1068x802.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07094725/2022-sc-bronson-559x420.jpg 559w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07094725/2022-sc-bronson-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07094725/2022-sc-bronson-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>In line with the mullet update, the suspension of the 2022 Santa Cruz Bronson is refined. Santa Cruz have altered the way the Bronson delivers that 150mm of rear wheel travel, with the next generation VPP link utilizing a longer stroke length shock.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-4\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07093420/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-mullet-rear-end.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07093420/2022-santa-cruz-bronson-mullet-rear-end.jpg\" alt=\"2022 santa cruz stays\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/ww