/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-297x145.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090535/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-800x390.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090535/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-120x59.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090535/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-768x374.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090535/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-696x339.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090535/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-1068x521.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090535/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-862x420.jpg 862w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090535/2022-Santa-Cruz-Bronson-geometry-mullet-533x261.jpg 533w\"></a></p><h4>Frame Details</h4><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock.jpg\" alt=\"2022 santa cruz bronson shock\" width=\"1200\" height=\"790\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-297x196.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-800x527.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-768x506.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-696x458.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-1068x703.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-638x420.jpg 638w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-297x196.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-800x527.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-768x506.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-696x458.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-1068x703.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07091457/santa-cruz-bronson-2022-frame-shock-638x420.jpg 638w\"></a></p><p>The 2022 Santa Cruz Bronson runs a 230mm x 60mm shock; it’s an air shock on all seven stock builds though Santa Cruz tell us there is plenty of room for a coil. The boost frame will accommodate 27.5″ tires with a width no greater than 2.6″, and a rear brake rotor no larger than 220mm.</p><p>The bike runs a threaded bottom bracket, a SRAM UDH hanger, and an IS headset with a 44mm upper and a 49mm external lower; thus, you could adjust the bike’s head angle with options from Wolf Tooth Components or Cane Creak if you wanted to slacken it off without also slackening the seat tube angle.</p><p>One set of bottle bosses sits within the front triangle but the frame does miss out on an accessory mounting point. Santa Cruz have thrown some frame protection in there with a rubber mold on the underside of the downtube and more on the driveside stays.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-large-leaderboard-2\"></span></p><h3>New Santa Cruz Carbon Handlebar</h3><figure id=\"attachment_261161\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261161\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090940/2022-santa-cruz-carbon-handlebar-35mm-riser.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090940/2022-santa-cruz-carbon-handlebar-35mm-riser.jpg\" alt=\"santa cruz carbon handlebar 35mm rise\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/07090940/2022-santa-cruz-carbon-handlebar-35mm-riser.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.a